folder: Hudson Street & North Moore Street, Manhattan, NY
original_title: Manhattan: Hudson Street - North Moore Street
text:
Hudson Street, north from(No. 129) but not including North Moore Street, showing the New York Central Railroad tracks and freight cars. The prominent building shown is the Green Industrial Building,at the S.W.
corner of Hubert Street.
July 26, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
